runs.comm: opens the face and steers him down to third man, good away movement
gets off the mark in the same way as Vijay, dabs him to third man
gets behind the line and defends towards extra cover
strays down the leg side and wide called, tried to steer it away
lands it outside off and he gets forward and shoulders arms
short down the leg side and he swivels quickly and pulls, rolls his wrists and the ball races to fine leg
Vijay fails yet again, Mpofu bowls a slower ball on the pads and Vijay tries to flick it away by using his wrists, picks out Utseya at short square leg, easy catch
drifts on the body and he tries to flick it away but the ball rolls to the on side
gets behind the line and defends to the off side
gives him width and he uses the movement to dab it down to third man
a direct hit would have sent him back! Raina squirts it to cover and sets off, Ojha doesn't want the run but he has to cooperate with his captain, the throw from Ervine was wide
gets forward and drives to mid-off
holds the length back outside off and he stays back and defends
cuts through the off side and third man runs across to mop up
stays back and punches it just wide of mid-off
stays back and defends back to the bowler
steers it towards point and tells his partner to wait, Ojha's in no great hurry

when in doubt, go for the short ball! No secret against India, Mpofu drops it short down the leg side and Ojha moves across his stumps and withdraws the shot, the ball appears to brush his glove, Taibu and the bowler know he's gone
lands outside off and he shoulders arms
fullish in length on middle and of and he drives uppishly towards mid-on
bangs it in short and Raina ducks under the bouncer
moves across his stumps slightly and clips it towards fine leg
swings away late and he pushes it softly towards cover
shuffles and he clips it towards fine leg off his hips
Raina breaks the shackles! It wasn't really that short, he stayed at the crease, waited for it and clubbed high over deep midwicket
Mpofu teases him with late movement, Rohit fishes at it outside off
and again, fuller this time and the late away movement has Rohit in a fix, fishes out side off
this one holds its line but Rohit doesn't offer a shot
strays on the pads and he clips it away through the gap between mid-on and midwicket
he bowls the bouncer this time and Rohit swings and misses, perhaps expecting it to be called a wide
classic cut, gives him width outside off and he rolls his wrists and slashes past the packed off side field, beats backward point
full on the off stump and driven straight to mid-off
keeps it straight and Raina is happy to push it straight to mid-off
fetches it from outside off and plays a half-hearted pull down to fine leg
he improvises and it works! Raina chips down the track to a good length ball and flat bats it along the ground past the diving extra cover fielder
he oversteps, Rainsford drops it a bit short again and Raina swivels and pounds it over midwicket, beats the fielder, one bounce and four
Free Hit he strays down the leg side and he swivels and pulls wide of the keeper, runs to fine leg
makes room but he's cramped up, chops it towards cover
pushes it straight to short midwicket
tossed up on the off stump and pushed towards long-on
makes room and cuts towards cover point
pushes it towards mid-on and the fielder does well to run across and intercept it
short and pulled away down to deep square leg
full on the pads and he pushes it back to the bowler
tucks it to the deep on the on side and they take the first run fast
he perishes going for the big hit, he comes down the track and tries to launch him over the on side, Chigumbura leaps up and takes the catch over his head
Game on here! Well done Taibu! Rohit gets forward to defend but the ball brushes his thigh and rolls towards Taibu, Rohit 's back foot was out of the crease and the alert Taibu whips off the bails
full on middle and leg and pushed down to long-on
tossed up on middle and leg, the ball brushes his pad and rolls away
pushes it to the off side
tossed up on middle and leg and pushed to the on side
take that! Tossed up on middle and leg and he stays at the crease and bludgeons it over long-on
drives it to long-off
turns it to midwicket for a single
he drops it short and Kohli goes right back and clubs it over midwicket
gets forward and drives straight to cover
tossed up on middle and leg and clipped to midwicket
turns it to midwicket
Chigumbura bangs it in short to Yusuf down the leg side and the batsman doesn't offer a shot
not quite the length to bowl to him, short outside off and he pulls in front of square and carts it over deep midwicket
stays behind the line and knocks it back to the bowler
stays at the crease and he tucks it to the on side
the slower bouncer outside off and Yusuf looks a bit silly as he tries to swat it and fails to connect
this time he connects! Short outside off and he swats that over extra cover, err in length against Yusuf and you will get spanked
pushes it down to long-on
full on the off stump and driven towards mid-off
glances it towards short fine leg
stays back and slaps it towards cover
full on the pads and he knocks it towards midwicket
strays down the leg side and wide called
full down the leg side and he clips it away towards fine leg, Ed Rainsford does brilliantly to slide to his right and cut it off
too ambitious with that bouncer, can't play that, wide called
good length on the off stump and he clips it to deep square leg
makes room and he scoops it high over wide long-off, lovely shot
pushes it towards mid-on
heaves it towards deep midwicket and Chibhabha had actually fielded it one handed at the boundary falling to his left, he falls and touches the rope, fab attempt though
turns it to short midwicket
turns it to short fine leg
full on middle and leg and he comes forward and lofts him over mid-on, one bounce and four
chips it in the air but checks his shot to long-off
drops it short outside off and he makes room and cuts past backward point
gets forward and pushes it down to long-on
tossed up on middle and leg, he turns it to fine leg
stays back and punches it to midwicket
bang! Slightly short and he goes back and smacks it over deep midwicket, wonderful bat speed
gets forward and pushes it towards long-on
makes room and forces it down to long-on
a single down to long-on and India have finally beaten Zimbabwe on tour
